These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: puzzles, board-games, sudoku, drawing, fishing, baking, dancing
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, british, chinese, dutch, egyptian, french, german
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, golf, skateboarding, surfing, swimming
House: modern, farmhouse, gothic-revival, art-deco, tower, townhouse, craftsman
 1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the dutch##1
 3. the tower house is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the british is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the german##1
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the craftsman house is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the art-deco house is between the craftsman house and the french##2
 9. the egyptian is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
10. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
12. the person who's hobby is fishing is the modern house##1
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the chinese##1
14. the french is the gothic-revival house##1
15. the townhouse house is on the left of the german##1
16. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
17. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the chinese##1
18. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the egyptian##1
19. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Hobby      | board-games  | baking        | fishing | sudoku      | drawing     | puzzles      | dancing     |
| Nationality   | british | dutch         | german   | australian | french    | egyptian | chinese |
| Sport         | cricket | skateboarding | baseball | basketball | swimming  | surfing  | golf    |
| House     | tower  | townhouse         | modern     | farmhouse    | gothic-revival | art-deco     | craftsman     |

