.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, lemonade, mirinda, tea
7 different pets are kept: hamster, snake, chinchilla, lizard, turtle, rabbit, ferret
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, disco, indie, metal, pop, reggae, rock
There are 7 different favourite colors: chestnut, coral, blood-red, amber, blue, brown, ivory
 1. the person drinking cola is the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 3. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 4. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 5. the person who likes brown is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the fan of rock is the person who likes ivory##1
 9. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the fan of metal is between the fan of indie and the owner of the ferret##2
11. the fan of disco is the owner of the lizard##1
12. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
13. the fan of pop is between the owner of the ferret and the fan of reggae##2
14. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
15. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
16. the person who likes ivory is on the far left##1
17. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
18. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
19. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
20. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person who likes brown and the owner of the snake##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |     4      |    5    |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | hot-chocolate | 7up      | iced-tea   | tea     | mirinda    | cola      |
